AddressInfo.Title: Wine & Heritage Hotel ROXANICH
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Winery, a la carte restaurant and boutique hotel- Roxanich Wine & Heritage hotel is a 32 units property in eclectic design reflecting the Italian 1960's aestethics.
The property features 2 EV charging units of up to 22 Kw each, located in the hotel garage. 
EV charging for all winery, restaurant and hotel guests free of charge.
